cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper discusses the application of fairness in machine learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). It also discusses open questions in implementing equality of opportunity, which is related to the field of cryptography (cs.CR) and the ethical considerations of using machine learning (cs.CY). The paper also proposes a new fairness metric, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and discusses improvements in model training, which is related to the field of systems and control (cs.SI).
